MENU_PKG_FOX
  Here you will find options for the Fox Toolkit

SDECFG_PKG_FOX_EXAMPLES
  This option enables the build of example applications, such as a calculator,
  a screenshot utility as well as a file browser. You most probably do not
  want those ...
